description: Attention entry-level buyers and empty-nesters looking to downsize- this is a rare offering- a 1-bed 1.5 bath condo with garage parking and an extra 780 square feet of lower-level, deeded space that can be used as a home office, gym, den, or all of the above, as it has a half bath and an HVAC unit. The main level features an open-concept living room, dining room, and kitchen, making it ideal for entertaining. Amenities and details include a natural wood-cabinet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a sunny and spacious bedroom, hardwood flooring, in-unit laundry, ample closet space, and an abundance of natural light that will uplift your spirits. This unit has its private entrance and a 1-car garage with a large overhead storage shelf. The property is conveniently located near all highways and within walking distance to the Red Line T, as well as all the Broadway shops and restaurants, ensuring you're always close to everything you need.
